Job_Description:
YOUR TASKS AND RESPONSIBILITIES

The primary responsibilities of this role, Release Train Engineer (RTE), are to:

Plan, organize and facilitate Agile Release Train (ART) ceremonies (e.g. program increment (PI) planning, ART sync, product owner (PO) sync, scrum of scrums, system demos, and inspect & adapts);
Coach delivery teams and scrum masters on agile and scrum practices;
Foster communities of practice, and promote the use of software engineering and quality best practices;
